  "description": "This project represents the method of constructing genetic map for the\n Panicum hallii Recombinant Inbreed Line (RIL) population. This population\n is a cross between one inland (HAL2) and one coastal (FIL2) natural\n accession of P. hallii. This map compromise of 441 RIL individuals\n genotyped for 901 markers.  The raw sequences  for RIL\n individuals are available in NCBI SRA archive Umbrella project\n PRJNA701489.  ",
